# Slide 1
;The Mozilla Project launched at Netscape on March 31, 1998, to offer choice to users and drive innovation on the Web.
Projekt Mozilla je započet preko Netscape-a 31. marta 1998. godine, kako bi se pokrenule inovacije na internetu i omogućio izbor njegovim korisnicima.


# Slide 2
;Proudly non-profit, Mozilla makes products like Firefox with a mission to keep the power of the Web in the hands of users everywhere.
Ponosna neprofitna organizacija, Mozilla pravi proizvode kao što je Firefox s ciljem očuvanja moći interneta u rukama korisnika širom svijeta.


# Slide 3. "The New York Times" is the proper name of an English publication and should not be translated.
;More than 10,000 contributors expressed their support for our mission by paying for a full-page ad in <cite>The New York Times</cite> on the day Firefox 1.0 launched in 2004.
Više od 10.000 saradnika izrazilo je svoju podršku za našu misiju tako što su finansirali reklamu preko cijele stranice u časopisu <cite>The New York Times</cite> na dan kada je Firefox 1.0 lansiran 2004. godine.


# Slide 4
;Today Mozilla has contributors on every continent, including Antarctica (where Firefox is used by 80% of people).
Danas Mozilla ima saradnike na svim kontinentima, uključujući i Antarktik (gdje Firefox koristi 80% ljudi).


# Slide 5
;Firefox Add-Ons allow you to customize and take control of your Web experience. Nearly 4 billion of them have been downloaded by users so far.
Firefox dodaci vam omogućavaju da prilagodite i preuzmete kontrolu nad svojim iskustvom na webu. Skoro 4 milijarde dodataka je do sada preuzeto od strane korisnika.


# Obsolete Slide 5 (DO NOT REMOVE)
;Firefox Add-Ons allow you to customize and take control of your Web experience. Over 3 billion of them have been downloaded by users so far.
Firefox dodaci vam omogućavaju da prilagodite i preuzmete kontrolu nad svojim iskustvom na webu. Skoro 3 milijarde dodataka je do sada preuzeto od strane korisnika.


# Slide 6
;Mozilla is leading the way in online privacy with browser innovations like Do Not Track and Lightbeam that give users greater control of their personal data.
Mozilla prednjači u internet privatnosti sa web pretraživačkim inovacijama kao što su funkcija Nemoj me pratiti i Lightbeam koji daju korisnicima veću kontrolu nad njihovim ličnim podacima.


# Slide 7
;Our global community has helped translate Firefox into over 70 languages, making the browser available to more than 90% of the world's population.
Naša globalna zajednica je pomogla da se Firefox prevede na preko 70 jezika, čineći ga dostupnim za 90% svjetske populacije.


# Slide 8
;In 2008, 8,002,530 people chose Firefox in a single day to set a Guinness World Record for “Most Downloads of a Software Application in 24 Hours.”
U 2008. godini 8,002,530 je odlučilo da preuzme Firefox na isti dan kako bi postavili Ginisov svjetski rekord za “Softversku aplikaciju sa najviše preuzimanja u 24 sata.”


# Slide 9
;The Mozilla Festival is our largest annual event, bringing together hundreds of creative minds to realize the full power and potential of the Web.
Mozilla festival je naš najveći godišnji događaj na kome se okupljaju stotine kreativnih umova kako bi realizovali punu moć i pun potencijal interneta.


# Slide 10
;Mozilla Webmaker works to create a more Web-literate planet, providing tools and projects to help people take greater control of their online lives.
Mozilla Webmaker radi na stvaranju web-pismenije planete. Obezbjeđujući alate i projekte kako bi pomogli ljudima da imaju veću kontrolu nad svojim životom na internetu.


# Slide 11
;Firefox for Android brings the Firefox desktop browsing experience to phones and tablets. Available on Google Play, it has been downloaded more than 80 million times.
Firefox za Android donosi iskustvo pretraživanja sa desktop Firefoxa na telefone i tablete. Dostupan je na Google Play, sa više od 80 miliona preuzimanja.


# Obsolete Slide 11 (DO NOT REMOVE)
;Mozilla leads the Open Badges program, an online standard that helps people gain recognition for 21st century skills and unlock new career opportunities.
Mozilla vodi Open Badges program, internet standard koji pomaže ljudima da dobiju priznanje za vještine 21-og vijeka i stvore nove prilike za zapošljavanje.


# Slide 12
;The Mozilla Developer Network is a community-driven Web resource that provides the best documentation, tutorials and tools available to more than 2 million visitors each month.
Mozillina mreža pogramera je internet resurs pokrenut zajednicom koja nudi najbolju dokumentaciju, uputstva i alate koji su dostupni za 2 miliona posjetilaca svakog mjeseca.


# Slide 13
;Mozilla works to care for and preserve the Web as a shared public resource for the benefit of everyone.
Mozilla radi na njegovanju i očuvanju interneta kao zajedničkog javnog resursa u službi svih.


# Slide 14
;In 2013, Mozilla launched Firefox OS to unleash the full power of the Web on smartphones and once again offer control and choice to a new generation of people coming online.
U 2013-oj, Mozilla je lansirala Firefox OS kako bi oslobodila punu moć interneta na pametnim telefonima i još jednom ponudila kontrolu i izbor novoj generaciji ljudi na internetu.


# Slide 15
;The work Mozilla does is made possible thanks to tens of thousands of volunteers who believe the Web should remain open and accessible to all.
Ono što Mozilla postiže je omogućeno zahvaljujući desetinama hiljada volontera koji vjeruju da web treba da ostane otvoren i dostupan svima.


